cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CL, cs.CV

This paper introduces a new abstraction called Think Again Networks (ThinkNet) which can be applied to any state-dependent function, such as a recurrent neural network. The paper focuses on the application of ThinkNet to neural networks and proposes a new loss function called the Delta Loss. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning) as the paper proposes a new approach to training neural networks. Other likely sub-categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.CV (Computer Vision) as the paper discusses the application of ThinkNet to various state-dependent functions.
